osCommerce 2.3.4.1 Migrating to PHP 7.x

Download for installation
https://github.com/ruden/oscommerce2/archive/2341-php7.zip

See the code
https://github.com/osCommerce/oscommerce2/compare/master...ruden:2341-php7

Migrating from PHP 5.6.x to PHP 7.0.x
http://php.net/manual/en/migration70.php

Migrating from PHP 7.0.x to PHP 7.1.x
http://php.net/manual/en/migration71.php

If you install add-on needs to be replaced
$HTTP_GET_VARS -> $_GET
$HTTP_POST_VARS -> $_POST
$HTTP_COOKIE_VARS -> $_COOKIE
$HTTP_SESSION_VARS -> $_SESSION
$HTTP_POST_FILES -> $_FILES
$HTTP_SERVER_VARS -> $_SERVER

Goodbye php5.x :)